Title: Clyde Bruckman's Final Repose
Plot: In the midst of a psychic sideshow while on a murder case, Mulder and Scully enlist the help of a man who may have a true psychic ability to foresee how people will die to help the agents catch a man killing fortune tellers.
GuestStars: Peter Boyle, Stu Charno, Frank Cassini, Dwight McFee, Japp Broeker, Greg Anderson, Alex Diakun, Karin Konoval, David McKay, Ken Roberts, Doris Rands
